  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><ul><li> Automatically detect foot and hand movements in animations and generate animation notifies</li><li> Easy to set up, with default values for the UE4 mannequin</li><li> Customisable detection for feet and hands (ground thresholds, positional vs speed weightings, etc)</li><li>Dynamic ground detection or manual ground height entry</li><li>Custom Unreal and FMOD studio notify classes, with further features including:</li><li>Ground surface detection - detect physical surfaces with a line trace fired from the bone</li><li>Movement strength detection</li><li>Surface angle detection</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Code Modules:</p><ul><li> AutoNotifyTool [Editor]</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Number of Blueprints: 2</p><p>Number of C&#43;&#43; Classes: 6</p><p>Network Replicated: No</p><p>Supported Development Platforms: Mac, Win64</p><p>Supported Target Build Platforms:</p><p>Documentation: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1X_UNnvWUZLTmueA6cj0EShiQstuFZpHH95v5tw8phDo/edit?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">Documentation</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/957192876\" rel=\"nofollow\">Basic Operation Video</a> | www.jmaud.io</p><p>Important/Additional Notes: FMOD Studio support is included through a complex runtime detection of the FMOD integration plugin, due to dependency and compile-time limitations of marketplace</p>",
